Aubrey Hruby bụ Co-Founder nke InsiderPR na onye na-etinye ego na mmalite Africa. Dị ka Senior Fellow na Atlantic Council na onye ndụmọdụ nye ndị na-etinye ego, ọ na-ekwu okwu ma na-ede akwụkwọ mgbe niile banyere nsogbu azụmahịa Afrịka na mgbasa ozi. Hruby enyewokwa ma nye ndụmọdụ na United States, ụlọ ọrụ gọọmentị na ndị na-eme iwu banyere azụmahịa na itinye ego na Africa.

Aubrey nọ na bọọdụ nke Invest Africa USA, ụlọ ọrụ ndụmọdụ nke ụlọ ọrụ nke Millennium Challenge Corporation (MCC) na ụlọ ọrụ Naịjirịa abụọ. Ọ bụ onye otu Council on Foreign Relations na Young Leader na Milken Institute.
Aubrey na-akụzi na Mahadum Georgetown ma bụrụ onye so dee akwụkwọ mmeri The Next Africa (Macmillan, 2015). O nwetara MBA na Wharton School na Mahadum Pennsylvania na MA na Mahadum Georgetown
